{"tid":1346409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家一齊寄] 鄭松泰法律顧問草擬投訴信　要求律師會嚴肅處理何君堯","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:39:10.000Z","uid":131171,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd21e54cc27350a5d2f960a4d30df9f4ab0e5ed","tid":1346409,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"昨晚流傳片段，見到建制派立法會何君堯讚揚元朗白衣人，熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰表示，他的律師草擬了一封投訴信，要求律師會嚴肅處理何君堯無視法紀，及違反律師守則和操守一事。 鄭松泰表示，大家只需要郵寄信件去律師會，不用填寫任何個人資料，強調量足夠多就是了。 鄭松泰續指，投訴在任何地方都可以做，請大家廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n//BY POST <br />\n<br />\nThe Law Society of Hong Kong <br />\n3rd Floor, Wing On House <br />\n71 Des Voeux Road Central <br />\nHong Kong <br />\n<br />\nDear Sirs <br />\nRe:    Complaint against Ho Kwan Yiu of Messrs. K.C. Ho &amp; Fong <br />\n<br />\nI am a citizen of Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\nAlthough I hold dear the civil rights of every citizen, the video footage widely spread on the news and the social media showing the interaction between Mr. Ho Kwan Yiu and a few men in white (with red ribbon on the wrist holding sticks) on 21st July 2019 shortly after the brutal attack happened in Yuen Long does call for an investigation into Mr. Ho, in particular, whether he was participated in the brutal attack in Yuen Long in any way. <br />\n<br />\nFurthermore, the widely spread photo taken by Mr. Ho himself within the Court building also calls for an investigation if not a reprimand against Mr. Ho&rsquo;s behaviour who is not only the officer of the Court but also a member of the Law Society of Hong Kong and has blatantly ignoring the law and wilfully putting himself above the law. <br />\n<br />\nI shall be very grateful if this esteemed society will take this complaint seriously. <br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully <br />\n<br />\nA Citizen<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-22-2019/54534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-22-2019%2F54534&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIHqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=d55c33dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-22-2019/54534</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"9383aaec88ad1242a397e9441101ad28d29c4fbc","tid":1346409,"uid":250443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 寫咗個白宮聯署<br />\nrequest國際人道救援/援助<br />\n已經有二萬三千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb673cfe29b7115f01aa3b68b00b48990fb4a537","tid":1346409,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a68c4a123f0caca9d529c88438ee8795cbabd2","tid":1346409,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e72c10947f5861568a228a0f7426d28b8212426","tid":1346409,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"蟲泰終於做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087cfeb29f3c7458c5b72ec139fd54a53691e9be","tid":1346409,"uid":108337,"like":1